FirstLoopStartFrameOffset: The offset into the beginning of the animation clip for the first loop of play.
StartFrameOffset: The offset into the beginning of the animation clip
EndFrameOffset: The offset into the end of the animation clip
PlayRate: The playback rate of the animation clip
SlotName: The slot name to use for the animation
bSkipAnimNotifiers: If on will skip sending animation notifies
bForceCustomMode: If on animation sequence will always play when active even if the animation is controlled by a Blueprint or Anim Instance Class
SwapRootBone: If on the root bone transform will be swapped to the specified root
bReverse: Reverse the playback of the animation clip
